{"tid":1587712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係時候諗下建立「香港社會」","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T19:36:05.000Z","uid":220009,"like":271,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4edcf05b1fe593e164ffc9c81ea9060dedb7d2","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"唔想聽到藍絲食店阿姐阿叔講廢話？<br />\n睇唔過眼你個藍絲老闆？<br />\n唔想日日見到藍絲鄰居？<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n建立黃絲社會，由你我開始！<br />\n<br />\n幫襯黃絲食店商店係第一步。<br />\n<br />\n逐步建立黃絲社交圈子。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲公司請番黃絲人，甚至係社運被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n甚至逐步買或租同一地區既樓。<br />\n<br />\n甚至自組民生議會。<br />\n<br />\n其他開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n我地未必能夠影響大公司，但係每一小步都好重要。<br />\n<br />\n無論今次係輸係贏，以上事情一定要做。<br />\n<br />\n香港人越團結，說話權就越大。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n<br />\nLinkage？香港人同香港人有Linkage有幾出奇啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要擁抱香港價值、文化和制度的，就是香港人！   BY 梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37107779f6679af36c9ce3abf0b4ca421b00e782","tid":1587712,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb76495ec18283d25cd58c3e33507c5d16f03b6","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0e0e9d23543b21a0b54e31323965a29a253bfcc9","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"95938ccaed3b109e38a6a13531b9ee6f3bafa92e","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0