id":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4edcf05b1fe593e164ffc9c81ea9060dedb7d2","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"唔想聽到藍絲食店阿姐阿叔講廢話？<br />\n睇唔過眼你個藍絲老闆？<br />\n唔想日日見到藍絲鄰居？<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n建立黃絲社會，由你我開始！<br />\n<br />\n幫襯黃絲食店商店係第一步。<br />\n<br />\n逐步建立黃絲社交圈子。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲公司請番黃絲人，甚至係社運被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n甚至逐步買或租同一地區既樓。<br />\n<br />\n甚至自組民生議會。<br />\n<br />\n其他開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n我地未必能夠影響大公司，但係每一小步都好重要。<br />\n<br />\n無論今次係輸係贏，以上事情一定要做。<br />\n<br />\n香港人越團結，說話權就越大。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n<br />\nLinkage？香港人同香港人有Linkage有幾出奇啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要擁抱香港價值、文化和制度的，就是香港人！   BY 梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"好計"},{"pid":"0bab83611526da1ba656ff056eec34753709d387","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"推到有人討論！<br />\n<br />\n獅子山下，互勵互勉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597ae4fad823fbec5397e9cbb1c8ff79dbe87dbc","tid":1587712,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9d735102ed157c85d4120d6df27e4c4f9e5f56","tid":1587712,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"人人為我，我為人人！<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔幫自己等邊個幫？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" clas