" /><br />\n<br />\n只要擁抱香港價值、文化和制度的，就是香港人！   BY 梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"咁首先你開一間公司先"},{"pid":"b8fe573d4446b2d3f7e0faa91514aced1e16ddc2","tid":1587712,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98771444f0392a772525dd5a2eaf79941a204dfe","tid":1587712,"uid":37528,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:05:32.000Z","msg":"贊成，長遠要咁先救到香港<br />\n可惜無黃色大商家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"所以咪要養囉,將大家必要既消費都放落黄色商家度,養養下就大嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee829a90a804927979763e8e205f2d057a5dc25b","tid":1587712,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98771444f0392a772525dd5a2eaf79941a204dfe","tid":1587712,"uid":37528,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:05:32.000Z","msg":"贊成，長遠要咁先救到香港<br />\n可惜無黃色大商家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"唔必要既消費就唔好洗,捐俾前線,或者儲起佢,長期戰,有排打.<br />\n不是因為有希望而堅持,是因為堅持才有希望."},{"pid":"9c0aa7cd958e69a346ea640a8e757ecf5a21797a","tid":1587712,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"社會資源不平衡，點實現香港社會"},{"pid":"8ae973393041cedc7edf915520054af26eec5852","tid":1587712,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"參考下西甲球隊畢爾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1035175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1035175&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=a18bcc6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1035175&h=76c3f7fd\" target=\"_blank\">htt